<div class="bottom"><span>BY ORDER OF THE OVERBOBBLE COUNCIL</span><br />
<span>The following file describes a Xerxes-Class humanoid entity receptacle, and is level 6/1730 classified. Viewer discretion is advised.</span></div>
<div class="bobble-bg"></div>
</div>
<br />
