<p><strong>Test Parameters:</strong> To determine the mental fortitude of the subject while having its face removed.</p>
<div class="content-log inset">
<p><strong>MTF-X76:</strong> We’re going to begin making the first incision now. Scalpel please-</p>
<p><strong>Subject-1833:</strong> Get your <em>fucking</em> hands off of me, you freaks. I swear to <em>god</em> I’ll-</p>
<p><strong>MTF-X76:</strong> Begin cutting.</p>
<p><strong>Subject-1833:</strong> Get away from me! Get- god, please, get- (<em>screaming</em>)</p>
<p><strong>MTF-X76:</strong> Please note the subject’s distress for the record.</p>
<p><strong>Subject-1833:</strong> No! (<em>Screaming</em>) Not my face! What is <em>wrong</em> with you?!</p>
<p><strong>MTF-X76:</strong> We’ll just do half today, and come back later to do the rest. The subject will require time to recover. (<em>Pauses</em>) Tell us, Ralph, would you say you’re feeling particularly mentally fortitudinous at this moment?</p>
<p><strong>Subject-1833:</strong> God <em>damn</em> you, you aesthetically challenging ass-</p>
<p><strong>MTF-X76:</strong> Fascinating. (<em>Pauses</em>) Hand me that bottle of bleach - we don’t want this getting infected.</p>
</div>
<p><strong>Test ID:</strong> #0004</p>
