<p><strong>Subject-1833:</strong> I don’t know what you think you’re doing, but nothing can be worse than the face thing. You played your hand too early.</p>
<p><strong>MTF-X76:</strong> The subject is restrained.</p>
<p><strong>MTF-X76:</strong> Let us begin.</p>
<p><em>Music begins playing over loudspeakers in the test chamber. The subject is seen writhing uncomfortably in its restraints.</em></p>
