<p><strong>MTF-X76:</strong> (<em>Collective laughter</em>) Tough nuts, Ralph. We’ll be back - eventually. Until then, our director will have this on repeat for you.</p>
<p><strong>Subject-1833:</strong> No! Please, god, no! Don't do this! Jesus Christ please somebody make it stop! I can't breathe!</p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div class="content-log">
<p><span style="font-size:120%;">MZL Testing Log</span><br />
<span style="font-size:80%;">Department of Pain and Suffering</span></p>
<hr />
